      "failure_message": "Requires tonic immobility with high threat and very low agency; keeps awareness online via an engagement floor and explicitly excludes dissociation; also excludes panic (high-arousal dysregulation) by capping panic and keeping arousal in the freeze band; gated by a freeze spike/crossing or a sharp drop in agency."
